data.description: This is truly a unique opportunity to own a home that's better than new. Totally updated kitchen with white cabinetry, beautiful mosaic backsplash and ceramic flooring. New hardwood flooring in the Living & Dining Rooms. Freshly painted throughout. Newly updated bath. This home really is move in ready with new furnace, upgraded electric box, security system, new roof, siding and concrete driveway. Bring your buyers - they won't want to miss this one. Pre-qualification and/or proof of funds required with all offers.
